deps.context: project(llvm   version 16.0.1   languages c cxx asm)

libs.content: find_program(gold_executable names ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld.gold ld.gold ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld ld doc "the gold linker")
find_program(ld64_executable names ld doc "the ld64 linker")
find_library(terminfo_libraries names terminfo tinfo curses ncurses ncursesw)

find_program(sphinx_executable
             names sphinx-build sphinx-build2
             doc "path to sphinx-build executable")

find_program(llvm_lit
                 names llvm-lit lit.py lit
                 paths "${llvm_main_src_dir}/utils/lit"
                 doc "path to lit.py")

find_program(llvm_lit
                   names llvm-lit lit.py lit
                   paths "${llvm_main_src_dir}/utils/lit"
                   doc "path to lit.py")

find_library(vtune_libraries libittnotify
    hints "${vtune_include_dirs}/.."
    paths ${dirs}
    path_suffixes lib32)
find_library(zlib names libz.a libzlibstatic.a z zlib libz names_per_dir)
find_library(zstd names libzstd.a libzstdstatic.a zstd names_per_dir)

find_library(curses names libcurses.a libncurses.a names_per_dir
      paths
        /usr/local/opt/ncurses/lib
        /opt/homebrew/opt/ncurses/lib)

find_library(clang_libraries
    names
      libclang-cpp.so.16
      clang-cpp-16.0
      clang-cpp160
      clang-cpp
    names_per_dir
    hints "${llvm_libdirs}"
    
    no_system_environment_path
    no_cmake_system_path
  )

find_library(clang_${_prettylibname_}_lib names ${_libname_} names_per_dir
      hints "${llvm_libdirs}"
      
      no_system_environment_path
      no_cmake_system_path
    )

find_library(lld_library names lld-16.0 lld160 lld names_per_dir
    hints ${llvm_libdirs}
    paths
        /usr/lib/llvm-16/lib
        /usr/local/llvm160/lib
        /usr/local/llvm16/lib
        /usr/local/opt/llvm@16/lib
        /opt/homebrew/opt/llvm@16/lib
)

find_library(lld_${_prettylibname_}_lib names ${_libname_} names_per_dir
            hints ${llvm_libdirs}
            paths
                ${lld_libdirs}
                /usr/lib/llvm-16/lib
                /usr/local/llvm160/lib
                /usr/local/llvm16/lib
                /usr/local/opt/llvm@16/lib
                /opt/homebrew/opt/llvm@16/lib
                /mingw64/lib
                /c/msys64/mingw64/lib
                c:/msys64/mingw64/lib)

find_program(llvm_config_exe
        names llvm-config-16 llvm-config-16.0 llvm-config160 llvm-config16 llvm-config names_per_dir
        paths
            "/mingw64/bin"
            "/c/msys64/mingw64/bin"
            "c:/msys64/mingw64/bin"
            "c:/libraries/llvm-16.0.0/bin")
